一是誰能夠接替當今的中共政權，特別是中國缺少民主文化。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n共匪滅亡之時五大軍區將領應該會自相殘殺，重演民初軍閥混戰，天下大亂，到時中華民國識做嘅應該效法孫中山統一中國，由台灣反攻大陸，我始終相信，全中國百姓都會恭迎中華民國嘅歸來！"},{"pid":"d8fb38e11c07a2b931dbc8af20c8d48aebaa4b94","tid":635361,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T06:02:19.000Z","msg":"梗係啦都未贏夠"},{"pid":"0ed34ec7a9f8dc0065379d9e1d11c667914551cc","tid":635361,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T07:05:16.000Z","msg":"獨裁國家都唔會走得遠"},{"pid":"ecdcf87ebc21e5c6160673e2d80a3fd93f39635d","tid":635361,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T07:06:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae91a61712b5bceb4d40306bea452b2a101241b8","tid":635361,"uid":41375,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"f26a42c39ff3d8ac5af51cdcd04437a15f0103c1","tid":635361,"uid":189,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T05:34:13.000Z","msg":"世上有咩政權係永垂不朽"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T07:08:03.000Z","msg":"日本"},{"pid":"345354eb13e02470ff8bbcedce726b932f4e0a45","tid":635361,"uid":34223,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T10:21:05.000Z","msg":"咁其實你都會死全家 不過唔係依家咁解啫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"947b95a2193da70fb23ca55342f2646b7d283b62","tid":635361,"uid":162535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"656208f9f3cbeb6ec6e2144756d7496762550df4","tid":635361,"uid":16055,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T05:24:08.000Z","msg":"....我睇歷史書都知啦<br />\n中國算係咁 <br />\n百零二百年朝代一定倒台<br />\n何況中共咁撚樣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T10:22:05.000Z","msg":"問題係班鬼佬真係唔知架"},{"pid":"2ee2fd9796268f35fed8ab0e052b8a9383ed6f41","tid":635361,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"345354eb13e02470ff8bbcedce726b932f4e0a45","tid":635361,"uid":34223,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-2